sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant AuthzPolicy as AuthorizationPolicy<br/>CUSTOM Action
    participant Authorino as Authorino Service<br/>50051/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VS as VirtualService
    participant Service as Model Registry Service<br/>8080/9090 TCP
    participant REST as REST Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as gRPC Container<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as Database<br/>5432/3306 TCP TLS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: External REST API Access (with Istio + Authorino)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/...<br/>Authorization: Bearer {k8s-token}<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>AuthzPolicy: Policy Check
    AuthzPolicy->>Authorino: External Auth Request<br/>gRPC/50051 mTLS<br/>Request Metadata
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview API<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Validate Token
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Token Valid: {user/SA}
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview API<br/>Check GET permission on service
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Allowed: true/false
    Authorino-->>AuthzPolicy: Decision: ALLOW/DENY

    alt Authorization Success
        AuthzPolicy->>VS: Forward Request
        VS->>Service: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (if ISTIO_MUTUAL)
        Service->>REST: HTTP/8080
        REST->>gRPC: gRPC/9090 localhost
        gRPC->>DB: SQL Query<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>TLS (if configured)
        DB-->>gRPC: Query Result
        gRPC-->>REST: Metadata Response
        REST-->>Service: HTTP Response
        Service-->>VS: Response
        VS-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443
    else Authorization Failure
        AuthzPolicy-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: Internal Service Access (without Istio)

    participant InternalClient as Internal Pod

    InternalClient->>Service: HTTP/8080 or gRPC/9090<br/>No encryption<br/>No auth
    Service->>REST: HTTP/8080
    REST->>gRPC: gRPC/9090 localhost
    gRPC->>DB: SQL Query<br/>TLS (if configured)
    DB-->>gRPC: Query Result
    gRPC-->>REST: Response
    REST-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>InternalClient: Response

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Operator as Operator Controller

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch ModelRegistry CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: CR Created/Updated
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>Create Service<br/>Create ServiceAccount
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Istio Resources<br/>(Gateway, VS, DR, AuthzPolicy)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig<br/>Create Role/RoleBinding
